---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Self-Scans — Verdandi Weaver
description: Slow, nervous-system aware reflection. Gentle returns to yourself.
permalink: /self-scans.html
---

<section class="hero container fade-up">
  <p class="t-eyebrow hero__eyebrow">Self-scans</p>
  <h1 class="t-h1 hero__title t-balance">A slow way to <em>listen inward.</em></h1>
  <p class="t-lead hero__lead t-pretty">These are not quizzes. They will not score you, fix you, or tell you anything you did not already half-know. They are quiet rooms for noticing — at your own pace.</p>
  <p class="t-body" style="margin-top: 1.5rem; opacity: .55; max-width: 540px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;">Each scan takes 4–8 minutes. There are no right answers. You can stop at any moment and come back later, or never. Both are fine.</p>
</section>

<section class="section section--sunk fade-up">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section-header">
      <p class="t-eyebrow">— Choose your room —</p>
      <h2 class="t-h2">What is asking for your attention?</h2>
      <span class="rule"></span>
    </header>
    <div class="grid grid-3">
      <a class="frame scan-frame" href="#start" onclick="event.preventDefault();startScan('nervous')"><p class="scan-frame__meta"><span class="scan-frame__dot"></span>5 minutes · 6 reflections</p><h3 class="t-h3">Nervous System Self-Scan</h3><p class="t-body">A gentle check-in with your current state — regulated, activated, withdrawn, or somewhere weaving between.</p><span class="link-chev link-chev--after scan-frame__cta">Begin softly</span></a>
      <a class="frame scan-frame" href="#start" onclick="event.preventDefault();startScan('burnout')"><p class="scan-frame__meta"><span class="scan-frame__dot"></span>7 minutes · 8 reflections</p><h3 class="t-h3">Burnout &amp; Fragmentation</h3><p class="t-body">Notice the small ways the self has been splitting itself across too many demands. Not to judge, only to see.</p><span class="link-chev link-chev--after scan-frame__cta">Begin softly</span></a>
      <a class="frame scan-frame" href="#start" onclick="event.preventDefault();startScan('awakening')"><p class="scan-frame__meta"><span class="scan-frame__dot"></span>6 minutes · 7 reflections</p><h3 class="t-h3">Social Awakening vs Soul Awareness</h3><p class="t-body">A subtle reflection on the difference between performing awareness and actually being changed by what you know.</p><span class="link-chev link-chev--after scan-frame__cta">Begin softly</span></a>
      <a class="frame scan-frame" href="#start" onclick="event.preventDefault();startScan('capacity')"><p class="scan-frame__meta"><span class="scan-frame__dot"></span>5 minutes · 6 reflections</p><h3 class="t-h3">Emotional Capacity Reflection</h3><p class="t-body">How much you can hold today, gently — without bypass, without performance. Just the truthful read.</p><span class="link-chev link-chev--after scan-frame__cta">Begin softly</span></a>
      <a class="frame scan-frame" href="#start" onclick="event.preventDefault();startScan('wholeness')"><p class="scan-frame__meta"><span class="scan-frame__dot"></span>8 minutes · 9 reflections</p><h3 class="t-h3">Grounded Wholeness Reflection</h3><p class="t-body">Where you currently sit on the long path back to your full, embodied, unsplit self. No verdict. Only a noticing.</p><span class="link-chev link-chev--after scan-frame__cta">Begin softly</span></a>
      <a class="frame scan-frame" href="#start" onclick="event.preventDefault();startScan('safety')"><p class="scan-frame__meta"><span class="scan-frame__dot"></span>6 minutes · 6 reflections</p><h3 class="t-h3">Relationship Safety Reflection</h3><p class="t-body">A tender look at the relationships you carry — where the safety is, where the asking is, and what your nervous system already knows.</p><span class="link-chev link-chev--after scan-frame__cta">Begin softly</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="start" class="section fade-up">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="scan" id="scan">
      <div class="scan__progress"><span id="scan-bar"></span></div>
      <div id="scan-step" class="scan__step">
        <p class="t-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);">A note before we begin</p>
        <p class="scan__q t-balance">There are no right answers.</p>
        <p class="scan__hint">Take your time. If a question doesn't resonate, skip it.</p>
        <div class="scan__opts">
          <button class="scan__opt" onclick="scanNext()">I'm ready · begin</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scan__nav">
        <span class="scan__count" id="scan-count">Intro</span>
        <button class="btn btn--link" onclick="scanReset()">Reset</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% block extraScripts %}
<style>
/* ── Scan cards ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.scan-frame__meta {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: .5rem;
  font-size: var(--text-xs, .75rem);
  opacity: .5;
  letter-spacing: .04em;
  margin: 0;
}
.scan-frame__dot {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 6px; height: 6px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: currentColor;
  opacity: .6;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.scan-frame__cta {
  margin-top: auto;
}

/* ── Reflection output ───────────────────────────────────────── */
.scan__reflection {
  max-width: 640px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.scan__reflect-label {
  font-size: var(--text-xs, .75rem);
  letter-spacing: .12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  opacity: .5;
  margin-bottom: var(--sp-4, 1.5rem);
  text-align: center;
}
.scan__reflect-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: var(--text-2xl, 1.75rem);
  font-weight: 400;
  margin-bottom: var(--sp-2, .5rem);
  line-height: 1.25;
}
.scan__reflect-sub {
  font-size: var(--text-sm, .875rem);
  opacity: .65;
  margin-bottom: var(--sp-6, 2.25rem);
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.scan__reflect-section {
  margin-bottom: var(--sp-8, 3rem);
}
.scan__reflect-eyebrow {
  font-size: var(--text-xs, .75rem);
  letter-spacing: .1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  opacity: .5;
  margin-bottom: var(--sp-3, 1rem);
}
.scan__reflect-p {
  font-size: var(--text-base, 1rem);
  line-height: 1.75;
  margin-bottom: var(--sp-4, 1.5rem);
  opacity: .88;
}
.scan__needs {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0 0 var(--sp-3, 1rem);
}
.scan__need {
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 1.25rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: var(--sp-2, .5rem);
  font-size: var(--text-base, 1rem);
  opacity: .88;
}
.scan__need::before {
  content: '·';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  opacity: .5;
}
.scan__needs-foot {
  font-size: var(--text-sm, .875rem);
  opacity: .5;
  font-style: italic;
}
.scan__reflect-closing {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: var(--text-lg, 1.125rem);
  line-height: 1.7;
  opacity: .9;
  margin-bottom: var(--sp-2, .5rem);
}
.scan__reflect-sig {
  font-size: var(--text-sm, .875rem);
  opacity: .45;
  margin-bottom: var(--sp-8, 3rem);
}
.scan__pathways-section {
  border-top: 1px solid currentColor;
  padding-top: var(--sp-6, 2.25rem);
  opacity: .9;
}
.scan__pathways-intro {
  font-size: var(--text-sm, .875rem);
  opacity: .55;
  margin-bottom: var(--sp-4, 1.5rem);
}
.scan__pathways {
  display: grid;
  gap: var(--sp-3, 1rem);
}
.scan__pathway {
  display: block;
  padding: var(--sp-4, 1.5rem);
  border: 1px solid currentColor;
  border-radius: var(--radius, .5rem);
  text-decoration: none;
  opacity: .85;
  transition: opacity .2s;
}
.scan__pathway:hover { opacity: 1; }
.scan__pathway-title {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: var(--text-base, 1rem);
  margin-bottom: var(--sp-1, .25rem);
}
.scan__pathway-blurb {
  display: block;
  font-size: var(--text-sm, .875rem);
  opacity: .6;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
@media (min-width: 600px) {
  .scan__pathways { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .scan__pathways .scan__pathway:last-child:nth-child(odd) { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
}
</style>
<script src="/assets/scan.js"></script>
{% endblock %}
